trans-unit.source: Specifies that SOAP messages sent to and from the method use <xref uid="langword_csharp_RPC" name="RPC" href=""></xref> formatting.
trans-unit.target: Angir at SOAP-meldinger sendt til og fra metoden Bruk <xref uid="langword_csharp_RPC" name="RPC" href=""> </xref> formatering.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute"></xref> class, setting all properties to their default values.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute"> </xref> klassen innstillingen alle egenskapene til standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the class, setting the property to the value of the action parameter.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den klasse, angi den egenskapen med verdien for den action parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The intent of the SOAP request.
trans-unit.target: Meningen i SOAP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute.Action*> property.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute.Action*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute.Action*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP header field of the SOAP request.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP-hodet felt i SOAP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the Action property is a URI indicating the intent of the SOAP request.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen er vanligvis en URI som angir meningen i SOAP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: However, the SOAP specification places no restrictions on the format and whether the URI refers to an existing document.
trans-unit.target: SOAP-spesifikasjon angir imidlertid ingen begrensninger på formatet og om URIEN refererer til et eksisterende dokument.

trans-unit.source: The presence and content of the Action property can be used by Web servers such as firewalls to appropriately filter SOAP request messages in HTTP.
trans-unit.target: Tilstedeværelse og innholdet i Action-egenskapen kan brukes servere som for eksempel brannmurer til å filtrere på riktig måte SOAP-forespørselsmeldinger i HTTP.

trans-unit.source: By default, the .NET Framework version 1.1 publishes the Action property in the `soapAction` attribute of the `soap:operation` element for each supported SOAP binding in WSDL documents generated for an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Som standard .NET Framework, versjon 1.1 publiserer Action-egenskapen i den `soapAction` for den `soap:operation` element for hver støttes SOAP-binding i WSDL-dokumenter som er generert for en XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The supported SOAP binding is SOAP 1.1.
trans-unit.target: Den støttede SOAP-bindingen er SOAP 1.1.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the SOAP specification, see the W3C Web site (http://www.w3.org/TR/SOAP).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om i SOAP-spesifikasjonen, kan du se W3C-webområde (http://www.w3.org/TR/SOAP).

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP header field of the SOAP request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP-hodet felt i SOAP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: The default is http://tempuri.org/MethodName where MethodName is the name of the XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er http://tempuri.org/MethodName der noe MethodName er navnet på XML Web service-metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the binding that an XML Web service method implements an operation for.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir binding som en XML-Web service-metoden skal implementere en operasjon for.

trans-unit.source: A binding, as defined by Web Services Description Language (WSDL), is similar to an interface in that it defines a concrete set of operations.
trans-unit.target: En binding er som er definert av Web Services (WSDL = Description Language), lik et grensesnitt ved at det definerer en konkret sett med operasjoner.

trans-unit.source: With respect to ASP.NET, each XML Web service method is an operation within a binding.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ASP.NET er hver XML Web service-metode en operasjon i en binding.

trans-unit.source: XML Web service methods are members of the default binding for an XML Web service or a binding specified within a <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> applied to an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: XML-metoder er medlemmer av standard bindingen for en XML-webtjeneste eller en binding som er angitt i en <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>brukes på en XML-webtjeneste.</xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: An XML Web service can implement multiple bindings, if multiple <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> attributes are applied to an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: En XML-webtjeneste kan implementere flere bindinger Hvis flere <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>attributtene er knyttet til en XML-webtjeneste.</xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Once one or more <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> attributes are applied to an XML Web service, a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> can be applied to individual XML Web service methods to indicate the binding operation implemented by a particular XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Når én eller flere <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>attributtene er knyttet til en XML-webtjeneste en <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>kan brukes på individuelle XML-metoder for å angi binding operasjonen implementeres av et bestemt XML Web service-metode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.Binding%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> to specify the binding an XML Web service method implements an operation for.
trans-unit.target: Angi <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.Binding%2A>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>en XML-Web service-metode implementerer en operasjonen setningen for. Hvis du vil angi bindingen</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: Only one <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> can be applied to an XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Bare én <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>kan brukes i en XML-Web service-metode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, an XML Web service method can only implement an operation for one binding.
trans-unit.target: Et XML-Web service-metoden kan derfor bare implementere en operasjon for én binding.

trans-unit.source: The binding an XML Web service method implements an operation for.
trans-unit.target: Bindingen en XML-Web service-metoden skal implementere en operasjon for.

trans-unit.source: The default is the name of the XML Web service with "Soap" appended.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er navnet på XML-webtjenesten med "Soap" legges.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether an XML Web service client waits for the Web server to finish processing an XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir om en XML-Web-tjenesteklienten venter på webserveren for å avslutte behandlingen av en XML-Web service-metode.

trans-unit.source: When an XML Web service method has the OneWay property set to `true`, the XML Web service client does not have to wait for the Web server to finish processing the XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Når en XML-Web service-metode har én vei-egenskapen satt til `true`, XML Web service-klienten har ikke å vente på webserveren for å avslutte behandlingen av XML-Web service-metoden.

trans-unit.source: As soon as the Web server has deserialized the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMessage>, but before it invokes the XML Web service method, the server returns an HTTP 202 status code.
trans-unit.target: Så snart nettserveren har deserialiseres i <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMessage>, men før den starter XML Web service-metoden, serveren returnerer en 202 HTTP-statuskoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMessage>

trans-unit.source: An HTTP 202 status code indicates to the client that the Web server has started processing the message.
trans-unit.target: En 202 HTTP-statuskode angir til klienten som nettserveren har begynt å behandle meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, an XML Web service client receives no acknowledgment that the Web server successfully processed the message.
trans-unit.target: Et XML-Web service-klienten mottar derfor ingen bekreftelse at nettserveren behandlet meldingen.

trans-unit.source: One-way methods cannot have a return value or any `out` parameters.
trans-unit.target: Enveis metoder kan ikke ha en returverdi eller noen `out` parametere.

trans-unit.source: If you are using the .NET Framework version 1.0 XML Web service methods that have either the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> attribute applied to them with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A> property set to `true`, do not allow access to their <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> using the static <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Current%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker de .NET Framework versjon 1.0 XML-metodene som har enten den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>attributtet som brukes med den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A>-egenskapen satt til `true`, ikke gir tilgang til sine <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>bruker statiske <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Current%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Current%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: To access the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>, derive the class implementing the XML Web service method from <xref:System.Web.Services.WebService> and access the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebService.Context%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Access den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>, avledet klasse som implementerer XML Web service-metoden fra <xref:System.Web.Services.WebService>og få tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.Services.WebService.Context%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.WebService.Context%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebService> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the XML Web service client does not wait for the Web server to completely process an XML Web service method; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis XML-webtjenesten klienten venter ikke nettserveren kan behandle fullstendig en XML-Web service-metoden. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the XML element associated with the SOAP response for an XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir XML-element som er knyttet til SOAP-svaret for en XML-Web service-metoden.

trans-unit.source: The ResponseElementName property defines the XML element used to encapsulate the parameters within the `Body` element of the SOAP response.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ResponseElementName definerer XML-elementet som omfatter parameterne i det `Body` element i SOAP-svaret.

trans-unit.source: The XML element associated with the SOAP request for an XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: XML-elementet som er knyttet til SOAP-forespørselen for en XML-Web service-metoden.

trans-unit.source: The default value is `WebServiceNameResult`, where `WebServiceName` is the name of the XML Web service method.

trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ResponseNamespace brukes i XSD-skjema for XML-Web service-metoden i tjenestebeskrivelsen.
